# 🧪 Salesforce QA Work Project

**Software QA Project | Salesforce Testing | Manual & API Testing**

Hello! This project is a **Salesforce CRM QA repository** containing test cases, workflows, and QA artifacts for modules like **Accounts, Contacts, Leads, and Opportunities**. It is designed to ensure smooth functionality and data accuracy in Salesforce.

---

## ✨ Project Highlights

- ✅ **Manual Testing** for Web + Salesforce CRM modules
- 🔗 **Salesforce Workflow Validation** (Accounts, Contacts, Leads, Opportunities)
- 📝 **Detailed Test Case Documentation** in Google Sheets
- 📸 **Screenshots** for visual reference
- 📊 **Bug Tracking & Reporting** using Jira
- 🤖 Ready for **Automation Preparation**

---

## 📂 QA Projects

- 📗 [Account Creation Test Cases (Google Sheet)](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/)
- 📘 [Lead Conversion Test Cases (Google Sheet)](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/)
- 📙 [Opportunity Flow Test Cases (Google Sheet)](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/)

> These links contain step-by-step QA scenarios and expected outcomes.

---

## 🧾 Test Case Overview

| Test Case ID | Module      | Description                  | Status |
|--------------|------------|------------------------------|--------|
| TC001        | Account    | Create a new Account         | ✅ Pass |
| TC002        | Contact    | Link Contact to Account      | ❌ Fail |
| TC003        | Lead       | Convert Lead to Opportunity  | ⏳ In Progress |

For the full list of test cases, please check the **Google Sheets** links above.

