## 🚀 Getting Started

1. **Clone the repository:**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/monikasarkar1809/Salesforce-QA-Work-Project.git
   ```
2. **Open the Google Sheets** to access detailed test scenarios.
3. Execute the test cases in Salesforce following the steps provided.

